trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona un agente de escucha que enruta toda la salida de la traza y la depuración a la infraestructura de IIS 7.0.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> clase conecta el mecanismo de seguimiento de [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] a [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase de agente de escucha permite a los programadores que crean [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] aplicaciones y que implementan la <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> y <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces para elevar el nivel de página, nivel de módulo o nivel de controlador de eventos para el [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infraestructura cuando el seguimiento está habilitada.

trans-unit.source: This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase de agente de escucha no se enruta [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] eventos a las clases ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Esto incluye la <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> clase y clases que implementan la <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> o <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaz.
